-- Seed data for local development / demo.
-- All statements are idempotent (ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING).

-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Banks
-- Each bank corresponds to a participant registered in the gateway's in-memory
-- registry and a mTLS client certificate generated by certgen.
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

