-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Sample transactions (transaction_view is a read-projection; in production
-- it is populated by the payment-processing flow, but seeding it directly
-- lets the portal dashboard show meaningful data from day one).
--
-- Amounts are in the minor unit of the payment currency (cents for USD/EUR,
-- pence for GBP).  Spread across the last 7 days to populate dashboard buckets.
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

